**My recommendation**: Start with **Priority 1** — connecting the LLM to the autonomous loop. That's the keystone. Everything else builds on having working end-to-end autonomy. Once the loop can think and act, the Guardian monitoring (P2), Watch Me recording (P3), and tests (P4) all become testable and meaningful.

